# Change keyboard keymap

```
loadkeys es
```

# Change font size


```
setfont ter-118b
setfont ter-128b
setfont ter-132b
```

To see al available fonts see `/usr/share/consolefonts`

# Mount luks encrypted data

```
cryptsetup open /dev/nvme0n1p2 recovery --type luks
vgscan
lvdisplay
vgchange -ay ArchVolGroup
mount /dev/mapper/recovery-root /mnt
```

To close it

```
umount /mnt
vgchange -an ArchVolGroup
cryptsetup close recovery
```

